<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3772733" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><b>1. 贝塞尔函数</b><br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/59c955c112eacc66584d548e66294c44_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="403" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/59c955c112eacc66584d548e66294c44_r.jpg">线性简化假设下的声压波动方程：</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="403" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/59c955c112eacc66584d548e66294c44_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/59c955c112eacc66584d548e66294c44_b.jpg">线性简化假设下的声压波动方程：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0e93810d97a36e50c196ec8960d9e65b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="197" data-rawheight="71" class="content_image" width="197"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="197" data-rawheight="71" class="content_image lazy" width="197" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0e93810d97a36e50c196ec8960d9e65b_b.jpg"><br>引入波数后就是亥姆霍兹方程：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/208feabdb8f341295e8b1368e41eca97_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="159" data-rawheight="52" class="content_image" width="159"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="159" data-rawheight="52" class="content_image lazy" width="159" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/208feabdb8f341295e8b1368e41eca97_b.jpg"><br>分离变量得：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/e88faff54af146c2582cd4b824cedb4e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="304" data-rawheight="49" class="content_image" width="304"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="304" data-rawheight="49" class="content_image lazy" width="304" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/e88faff54af146c2582cd4b824cedb4e_b.jpg"><br>柱坐标下的拉普拉斯算符变为： <br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1c4e2ab8af474f61be151efa5d698cd4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="391" data-rawheight="80" class="content_image" width="391"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="391" data-rawheight="80" class="content_image lazy" width="391" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1c4e2ab8af474f61be151efa5d698cd4_b.jpg"><br>代入并消去常量得：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/14bfc059902f4a1438d2661415814597_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="438" data-rawheight="79" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="438" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/14bfc059902f4a1438d2661415814597_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="438" data-rawheight="79" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="438" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/14bfc059902f4a1438d2661415814597_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/14bfc059902f4a1438d2661415814597_b.jpg"><br>发现这就是个贝塞尔方程，其解即贝塞尔函数。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5eb446618b1095833dbdd2c502e75b0e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="488" data-rawheight="98" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="488" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5eb446618b1095833dbdd2c502e75b0e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="488" data-rawheight="98" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="488" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5eb446618b1095833dbdd2c502e75b0e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5eb446618b1095833dbdd2c502e75b0e_b.jpg"><br>是以圆柱形流场中的径向声压分布为：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/9f45a9a14c130320897fa9768f2eaf6d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="287" data-rawheight="60" class="content_image" width="287">Jm/Nm分别是m阶第一/二类贝塞尔函数。</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="287" data-rawheight="60" class="content_image lazy" width="287" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/9f45a9a14c130320897fa9768f2eaf6d_b.jpg">Jm/Nm分别是m阶第一/二类贝塞尔函数。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/aec17d1e2de2fbde00a0fc88659e8021_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="363" data-rawheight="422" class="content_image" width="363"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="363" data-rawheight="422" class="content_image lazy" width="363" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/aec17d1e2de2fbde00a0fc88659e8021_b.jpg"><br>工程应用：航空发动机内部噪声计算<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0544793c655cb6bad8d65120df37727f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="929" data-rawheight="694" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="929" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0544793c655cb6bad8d65120df37727f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="929" data-rawheight="694" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="929" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0544793c655cb6bad8d65120df37727f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/0544793c655cb6bad8d65120df37727f_b.jpg"><br><br><b>2. 超几何函数</b><br><br>非牛顿流体的管道流量-压差关系, F1是阿佩尔超几何函数，2F1是超几何函数。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/7b6f1fbfc4c5a9e07897242e1bf76109_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="844" data-rawheight="423" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="844" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/7b6f1fbfc4c5a9e07897242e1bf76109_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="844" data-rawheight="423" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="844" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/7b6f1fbfc4c5a9e07897242e1bf76109_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/7b6f1fbfc4c5a9e07897242e1bf76109_b.jpg"><br><br><b>3. 椭圆函数</b><br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/9165217171428d0b54b4b8ad7a38db67_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="763" data-rawheight="427" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="763" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/9165217171428d0b54b4b8ad7a38db67_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="763" data-rawheight="427" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="763" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/9165217171428d0b54b4b8ad7a38db67_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/9165217171428d0b54b4b8ad7a38db67_b.jpg"><br>描述水面行波的KdV方程：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/46ce4c9bbdb3d9a69c6140ff6c56684a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="249" data-rawheight="45" class="content_image" width="249"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="249" data-rawheight="45" class="content_image lazy" width="249" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/46ce4c9bbdb3d9a69c6140ff6c56684a_b.jpg"><br>解析解：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/32bf816621d3a4054fb464797f05a3f8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="358" data-rawheight="46" class="content_image" width="358">其中cn就是个雅可比椭圆函数。</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="358" data-rawheight="46" class="content_image lazy" width="358" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/32bf816621d3a4054fb464797f05a3f8_b.jpg">其中cn就是个雅可比椭圆函数。


